an>\\\\(252\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_JIWUGBLTON\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(924\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisez la formule des combinaisons \\\\( C_n^k = \\\\frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!} \\\\).', 'hint')\"> ‚ùì Indice  </button> <div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">   <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span> </div>  <div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'On applique \\\\( C_{12}^{5} = \\\\frac{12!}{5!(7!)} = 792 \\\\).', 'explanation')\"> üí° Explication  </button> <div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">   <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span> </div>\n\n\n\n\n## Question 7\n\nUn comit√© de \\\\(10\\\\) ONG vote une d√©cision o√π chaque organisation a \\\\(40\\\\%\\\\) de chances de voter ¬´ pour ¬ª, de fa√ßon ind√©pendante. Quelle est la probabilit√© que \\\\(4\\\\) ONG votent en faveur ?\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_CGDJVPHXSD'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CGDJVPHXSD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.20\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CGDJVPHXSD\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.25\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CGDJVPHXSD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.30\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CGDJVPHXSD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.35\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisez la formule binomiale \\\\( P(X = k) = C_n^k p^k (1-p)^{n-k} \\\\).', 'hint')\"> \n‚ùì Indice \n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'La distribution binomiale donne \\\\( P(X=4) = C_{10}^{4} (0.4)^4 (0.6)^6 = 0.25 \\\\).', 'explanation')\"> \nüí° Explication \n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n## Question 8\n\nDans une organisation internationale, \\\\(20\\\\%\\\\) des propositions de r√©forme sont accept√©es apr√®s un premier examen. Quelle est la probabilit√© que parmi \\\\(8\\\\) propositions, au moins \\\\(2\\\\) soient accept√©es ?\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_XOUOLQXNVW'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_XOUOLQXNVW\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.567\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_XOUOLQXNVW\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.497\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_XOUOLQXNVW\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.852\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_XOUOLQXNVW\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.912\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Calculez \\\\( 1 - P(X=0) - P(X=1) \\\\) avec la loi binomiale.', 'hint')\"> ‚ùì Indice </button> <div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">   <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span> </div>  <div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'On applique \\\\( P(X\\\\geq2) = 1 - P(X=0) - P(X=1) \\\\) avec la distribution binomiale pour obtenir environ \\\\(0.497\\\\).', 'explanation')\"> üí° Explication </button> <div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">   <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span> </div>\n\n\n## Question 9\n\nUn organisme international organise une √©lection avec \\\\(3\\\\) candidats. Chaque votant choisit ind√©pendamment un candidat avec une probabilit√© de \\\\(0.4\\\\) pour le premier candidat, \\\\(0.25\\\\) pour le deuxi√®me et \\\\(0.35\\\\) pour le trois√®me candidat. Quelle est la probabilit√© que le premier candidat obtienne exactement \\\\(5\\\\) votes sur \\\\(10\\\\) ?\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_CBGTFKARYD'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CBGTFKARYD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.15\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CBGTFKARYD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.25\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CBGTFKARYD\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.20\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CBGTFKARYD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.30\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Utilisez la loi binomiale avec \\\\( n = 10, k = 5, p = 0.4 \\\\).', 'hint')\"> ‚ùì Indice </button> <div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">   <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span> </div>  <div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'On applique \\\\( P(X=5) = C_{10}^{5} (0.4)^5 (0.25+0.35)^5 \\\\) qui donne environ \\\\(0.20\\\\).', 'explanation')\"> üí° Explication </button> <div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">   <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span> </div>\n\n\n\n## Question 10\n\nSoit \\\\(X\\\\) une variable al√©atoire avec \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 2\\\\), que vaut \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(2X+1)\\\\)?\n\n\n\n::